{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3d69a9360a","title":"邓小平在研究××省委领导班子会议上的插话","origin":"清华大学、北京大学材料组编《邓小平言论摘录（续编）》，一九七六年四月","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6dc072f3cc","index":0,"year":1975,"month":10,"day":12,"articleId":"3d69a9360a"}],"tags":[{"id":"5bd9678625","name":"邓小平","type":"人物"},{"id":"5f6c7e74b5","name":"派性","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"f0e44655bb","name":"邓小平"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"223f3cdb0d","type":"title","text":"邓小平在研究××省委领导班子会议上的插话","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3d69a9360a"},{"id":"2fc2195441","type":"authors","text":"邓小平","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3d69a9360a"},{"id":"bf49095f27","type":"paragraph","text":"邓小平在研究××省委领导班子会议上的插话，一九七五年十月十二日（摘录）","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3d69a9360a"},{"id":"39c330d13a","type":"paragraph","text":"省委书记中的青年人下放去当县委副书记，对他们有好处，在上面架空是害了这些人。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3d69a9360a"},{"id":"37007536d4","type":"paragraph","text":"这个新的班子是中上，不弱。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3d69a9360a"},{"id":"b9a2e98fdb","type":"paragraph","text":"领导班子选准后要相对稳定，要使用适当，才能发挥作用。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3d69a9360a"},{"id":"a4b2d78b7f","type":"paragraph","text":"群众运动这一关（指批派性）不搞不行。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3d69a9360a"},{"id":"7ca70be7b2","type":"paragraph","text":"首先要把组织部的干部选好，要公道，党性强，敢字当头。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3d69a9360a"},{"id":"6e56238ed4","type":"paragraph","text":"对军队干部要管得很严，还搞派性的就调离、降职。要告诉他们继续搞派性那是犯罪。对于拿武器的人，不严格管理那还得了？军队干部有派性的，以调离省为宜，特别是军师级，不能留原地。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3d69a9360a"},{"id":"4c0fc8be81","type":"paragraph","text":"派头怕群众。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3d69a9360a"},{"id":"6c06fd140a","type":"paragraph","text":"总之，××省要开展一个反派性的群众运动。地、市班子，你们还要好好研究调整。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3d69a9360a"},{"id":"718aaf401c","type":"paragraph","text":"","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3d69a9360a"}],"page":{"id":"52c7d16223","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3d69a9360a","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}